snippet.title: Resident Evil Revelations PS4 / X1 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Resident Evil Revelations is available now for PS4 and Xbox One! Explore events that take place between Resident Evil 4 and Resident Evil 5, and untangle a web of lies and deceit.
